420
0:17:13.26,000 --> 0:17:15,000
One great challenge of modern life

421
0:17:15.26,000 --> 0:17:18,000
is to find the staircase amid all the clutter

422
0:17:18.26,000 --> 0:17:21,000
and then to do something good and noble

423
0:17:21.26,000 --> 0:17:24,000
once you climb to the top.

424
0:17:24.26,000 --> 0:17:27,000
