429
0:17:36.26,000 --> 0:17:38,000
because people are not purely selfish.

430
0:17:38.26,000 --> 0:17:4,000
Most people long to overcome pettiness

431
0:17:40.26,000 --> 0:17:42,000
and become part of something larger.

432
0:17:42.26,000 --> 0:17:45,000
